premise_source_doc_sentence: After the Eagles broke up in 1980 , Henley pursued a solo career and released his debut album I Ca n't Stand Still , in 1982 .
He has released five studio albums , two compilation albums , and one live DVD .

Since 2000 BYO has released albums by Pistol Grip , Manic Hispanic , Filthy Thieving Bastards , The Unseen , Sixer , One Man Army , Consumed , Throw Rag , The Business , The Briefs , Clit 45 , A Global Threat , Wednesday Night Heroes , and others .
